(US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/msPutPropertyEnabled\"><code>msPutPropertyEnabled()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/removeProperty\"><code>removeProperty()</code></a></li><li><em><code>setProperty()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for CSSOM</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSS\"><code>CSS</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframeRule\"><code>CSSKeyframeRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframesRule\"><code>CSSKeyframesRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule\"><code>CSSMediaRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNamespaceRule\"><code>CSSNamespaceRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSPageRule\"><code>CSSPageRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSRuleList\"><code>CSSRuleList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleRule\"><code>CSSStyleRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleSheet\"><code>CSSStyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSSupportsRule\"><code>CSSSupportsRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CaretPosition\"><code>CaretPosition</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Screen\"><code>Screen</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet\"><code>StyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StyleSheetList\"><code>StyleSheetList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TransitionEvent\"><code>TransitionEvent</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><strong><code>CSSStyleDeclaration.setProperty()</code></strong> 方法接口为一个声明了 CSS 样式的对象设置一个新的值&nbsp;。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\"><em>style</em>.setProperty(<em>propertyName</em>, <em>value, priority</em>);</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><em><code>propertyName</code></em>&nbsp;是一个&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> ，代表被更改的 CSS 属性。</li>\n <li><em><code>value</code></em><span class=\"badge inline optional\">可选</span> 是一个&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> ，含有新的属性值。如果没有指定，则当作空字符串。\n  <ul>\n   <li>注意:&nbsp;<em><code>value</code></em>&nbsp;不能包含&nbsp;<code>\"!important\"</code>&nbsp;--那个应该使用&nbsp;<em><code>priority</code></em> 参数。</li>\n  </ul>\n </li>\n <li><em><code>priority</code></em><span class=\"badge inline optional\">可选</span> 是一个&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> 允许设置&nbsp;\"important\" CSS 优先级。如果没有指定，则当作空字符串。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回值","title":"返回值","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/undefined\"><code>undefined</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"异常","title":"异常","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code></a> (NoModificationAllowedError)： 如果属性或装饰块为只读的，抛出此异常。</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>JavaScript 有一个特别的，更简单的在 CSSStyleDeclaration 对象上设置 CSS 属性值的语法：</p>\n\n<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>style</em>.cssPropertyName = 'value';</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下面的 Javascript 代码为一个选中元素样式的&nbsp;<code>margin</code>&nbsp;属性设置一个新的值：</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> declaration <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>styleSheets<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>rules<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ndeclaration<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setProperty</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'margin'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'1px 2px'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Equivalent to:</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// declaration.margin = '1px 2px';</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"说明","title":"&nbsp; 说明","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">描述</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状态</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">注释</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom/#dom-cssstyledeclaration-setproperty\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Object Model (CSSOM)<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">CSSStyleDeclaration.setProperty()</small></a></td>\n   <td>工作草案</td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Style/css.html#CSS-CSSStyleDeclaration\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 Style Specification<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">CSSStyleDeclaration</small></a></td>\n   <td>被废弃</td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>","titleAsText":"  说明"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容","id":"浏览器兼容","isH3":false,"query":"api.CSSStyleDeclaration.setProperty","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/setProperty/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"&nbsp; 说明","id":"说明"},{"text":"浏览器兼容","id":"浏览器兼容"}],"summary":"CSSStyleDeclaration.setProperty() 方法接口为一个声明了 CSS 样式的对象设置一个新的值 。","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CSSStyleDeclaration.setProperty()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CSSStyleDeclaration.setProperty()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/cssstyledeclaration/setproperty","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/cssstyledeclaration/setproperty/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration","title":"CSSStyleDeclaration"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/setProperty","title":"CSSStyleDeclaration.setProperty()"}],"pageTitle":"CSSStyleDeclaration.setProperty() - Web API